Before any actions please check this link: https://developer.android.com/training/basics/supporting-devices/languages.html

How to add new localization:
1. Copy 'values' directory as 'values-YOUR_LOCALE_CODE', locale codes examples: en, es, fr, uk, ru.
2. Translate the texts in the xml files in your locale's 'values' directory.
3. Make pull request.
4. PROFIT